    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it garaged and polished every single week. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next big adventure. You seriously won't find another one this clean! Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look and see for yourself!",
