    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality masterpiece that defies its age. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, and it shows in every square inch. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like luster with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in 'factory-fresh' state; the premium leather is supple and matte, free of any creases or wear, and still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the ambient lighting, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It features a comprehensive, documented service history with every scheduled maintenance performed ahead of time at authorized centers. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage is free from any debris or oxidation. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
